.TH JOUSTIX 6 "July 2026" "joustix 0.1.0" "Games"
.SH NAME
joustix \- flying-joust arcade game for Kitty-protocol terminals
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B joustix
.RI [ option ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Joustix renders a software framebuffer directly in Kilix or another terminal
implementing the Kitty graphics protocol. Fly above enemy riders, defeat them
in height-based collisions, and collect their eggs before they hatch.
.SH CONTROLS
Left/A and Right/D fly horizontally. Up/W/Space flaps. P or Escape pauses.
M toggles sound. Direction keys select menu options; Enter confirms the
selection. Q quits.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --selftest [seed] [ticks]
Run a deterministic headless simulation.
.TP
.B --rules-test
Run deterministic gameplay regressions.
.TP
.B --render-test [seed]
Write four PPM scene snapshots.
.TP
.B --sound-test
Play the procedural sound cues.
.TP
.B --help
Show command-line help.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B JOUSTIX_SKIP_PROBE
Skip the Kitty graphics capability query when set.
.TP
.B JOUSTIX_RENDER_DIR
Destination directory for render-test snapshots.
.TP
.B JOUSTIX_ASSETS
Override the production-image directory.
.SH AUTHORS
Joustix contributors.
